<div style="font-family: Helvetica, arial, sans-serif">
  <p>Hello!</p>

  <p>{{order.user.organization}} wants to make the following change to their order scheduled
    {{#is order.type 'pickup' 'courier'}}
      for pickup at {{timepart order.pickup_datetime}} on {{datepart order.pickup_datetime}}.
    {{else}}
      for delivery at {{timepart order.datetime}} on {{datepart order.datetime}}.
    {{/is}}
  </p>

  <blockquote style="background: #f9f9f9; border-left: 5px solid #ccc; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 10px;">{{options.changedDescription}}</blockquote>

  <p>Here is your updated order reflecting that change: <a href="{{config.baseUrl}}/manifests/manifest-{{order.id}}.pdf?review_token={{order.review_token}}">{{config.baseUrl}}/manifests/manifest-{{order.id}}.pdf</a></p>

  <p>PLEASE CONFIRM that you have received this email by replying!</p>

  <p>Thanks,</p>

  <strong>Patrick Mugavin</strong>
  <div>Concierge Specialist | Goodybag</div>
  <div>tel: {{phoneNumber config.phone.support}} </div>
  <div>PatrickMugavin@goodybag.com | goodybag.com</div>
</div>
